{"tid":56271,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"而家d服務業年輕人服務客人時西口西面","createTime":"2016-12-27T06:15:10.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-27T11:46:11.000Z","uid":40470,"like":2,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9e5d0cea80222dd65a8b132f7b499647a10087f2","tid":56271,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T06:15:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n屌你咁唔鍾意做你咪辭職囉<br />\n<br />\n你老細拎支槍指住你迫你返工咩？<br />\n<br />\n返工西口西面我做客既見到你就嬲<br />\n<br />\n你又無撚用唔讀好d書<br />\n<br />\n你又投錯胎無父幹<br />\n<br />\n你又生得唔靚做唔到明星<br />\n<br />\n所以你就應該接受現實<br />\n<br />\n返你時薪四十既工啦<br />\n<br />\n後悔點解當日唔讀好d書啦柒頭<br />\n<br />\n利申：<br />\n<br />\n頭先食飯屌柒左個態度差後生仔waiter<br />\n<br />\n做waiter學人扮型剷個all back頭<br />\n<br />\n屌你咁型就做明星啦<br />\n<br />\n做乜撚野waiter"},{"pid":"2f95f8ba94ede48bff019ba704e98b7cef0efb2c","tid":56271,"uid":11019,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T06:17:10.000Z","msg":"香港客"},{"pid":"4c105871f4b43d9f3f4634de37bdd695dabe45a0","tid":56271,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T06:17:41.000Z","msg":"個樣差唔多三十歲<br />\n<br />\n又好似好唔撚甘心做waiter既死款<br />\n<br />\n咁撚叻你又唔做老細？<br />\n<br />\n無撚用<br />\n<br />\n下次再去食就再大大力屌柒佢"},{"pid":"6c75142c274a0aee3f61e06b163d35dc21f0eea1","tid":56271,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T06:19:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>香港客</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n無乜野特別要求<br />\n<br />\n只係要兩杯水<br />\n<br />\n叫左佢兩次佢先死死地氣拎來<br />\n<br />\n仲要大力掉落枱面學人發圍<br />\n<br />\n我即係大聲屌柒佢<br />\n<br />\n屌到佢老細出埋來一齊道歉"},{"pid":"77ce42d9d7e1ee4362a8b49108b1a8f5e2256b75","tid":56271,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T06:26:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/l